                ],
            "effects": [
                "flamin'",
                "aromatic"
                ]
        },
        "boil": {
            "modes":[
                "at high heat for only a few minutes, for flavour, I like to boil in $liquid$, but you should use what you feel mathes best.",
                "at high heat for anywhere between 2-5 hours, just make sure to stir and taste once every half hour. Now I'll add that boiling in $liquid$ really gives the best taste and tenderness. Just saying."
