        "stew": {
            "modes":[
                "at around 100-120 degrees. The exact temperature does not matter much, as you should really just let it simmer unil it is done and delicious",
                "at a slow simmer for around 2 - 4 hours, dependent on the size. Calculate around half an hour pr. kg."
